the kevin bishop show was a sketch comedy written by and starring english comedian kevin bishop , part of the star stories team .   the show was commissioned by channel 4 for a six-part series starting on 25 july 2008 at 10 pm .   a pilot was broadcast on 23 november 2007 as part of channel 4 's comedy showcase and the programme soon earned interest for its incredibly fast pace ; 42 sketches were shown in 23 minutes .   the show was nominated for best new comedy at the 2008 british comedy awards .   the show started its second series on friday 31 july 2009 at 10 pm on channel 4 .